title: SEI to Announce Third-Quarter 2015 Earnings on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015
text:
October 15, 2015 09:00 ET SEI to Announce Third-Quarter 2015 Earnings on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015 
Public Invited to Monitor Conference Call at 2 p.m. Eastern Time 
OAKS, PA--(Marketwired - Oct 15, 2015) - SEI Investments Company ( NASDAQ : SEIC ) announced today that it intends to release earnings for the third-quarter 2015 on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, before the market opens. The company will hold a conference call to discuss these financial results beginning at 2 p.m. Eastern time. 
The public is invited to listen to the call at seic.com/investors . The live webcast may also be accessed at many financial services websites, including Google Finance and Yahoo Finance. 
Replays will be available shortly after the call at the above websites and also at (USA) 800-475-6701; (International) 320-365-3844; Access Code: 371051. 
About SEI SEI ( NASDAQ : SEIC ) is a leading global provider of investment processing, investment management, and investment operations solutions that help corporations, financial institutions, financial advisors, and ultra-high-net-worth families create and manage wealth. As of June 30, 2015, through its subsidiaries and partnerships in which the company has a significant interest, SEI manages or administers $661 billion in mutual fund and pooled or separately managed assets, including $262 billion in assets under management and $399 billion in client assets under administration. For more information, visit seic.com . Contact Information
